### Get current profile
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List users
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update profile
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo User",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "phone": "+50588887777",
  "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatars/demo.png"
}

### Change password
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password",
  "newPassword": "NewStrongPassword123"
}
